{"tid":2337552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三青年男女被控非法集結　拘捕警長認港鐵站未封　亦可能有乘客下車","createTime":"2020-12-23T11:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T11:52:20.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04caf49a45fd7ea513e60fc02d7b2406a47ca3a0","tid":2337552,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:05:48.000Z","msg":"去年 8 月 24 日的觀塘遊行演變成警民衝突，3 名年輕男女被控在黃大仙龍翔道非法集結，當中 19 歲男生另被指藏雷射筆，遭控一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪。案件今（23 日）在觀塘裁判法院續審。拘捕第三被告的警員否認辯方所指被告從未掙扎，但<span class=\"red\">承認當時路面有其他因車輛停駛而下車的司機及乘客，亦不清楚被告從何處到達現場</span>。控方案情完畢，裁判官屈麗雯裁定表證成立，辯方初步表示三名被告不會作供。案件明早續審。"},{"pid":"f3c64e7ff1d48546028916335d5f17e420f1a09b","tid":2337552,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/8-24-%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99-%E4%B8%89%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E8%AA%8D%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99%E6%9C%AA%E5%B0%81-%E4%BA%A6%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E4%B8%8B%E8%BB%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-24-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25B0%2581-%25E4%25BA%25A6%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25BB%258A%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=fc51342f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-24-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB